1. *Vama* je potrebna pomoć (You need help)
2. Oni su vam odlučili pomoći (They have decided to help you)
3. Da li vam je lakše sada? (Is it easier for you now?)
4. Oni će vama dati potporu (They will give you support)
5. *Vama* je to potrebno (You need it)
6. Oni će vam dati dobre savete (They will give you good advice)
7. Da li će vam to biti od koristi? (Will it be beneficial to you?)
8. Oni će vam dati pravu informaciju (They will give you the right information)
9. *Vama* je potrebno više vremena (You need more time)
10. Oni će vam dati potrebnu podršku (They will provide you with the necessary support)